text: Novy Sad () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Enemskoye Urban Settlement of Takhtamukaysky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 1337 as of 2018. There are 13 streets. == Geography == The khutor is located near Enem. == References == Category:Rural localities in Takhtamukaysky District
title: Novy Sad
